The local swimming association obtained a special incentive
award for its performance at the Hong Kong and Beijing legs of
this year's FINA World Cup short-course swimming series, at which
swimmers from the SAR improved at least 10 local records.
</P>
<P>
The total sum of 679,500 HK dollars (87,100 U.S. dollars) was
the biggest-ever awarded by the local Olympic committee. 
</P>
