international studies, said that hegemony of any country must not
be allowed to take over the international economic order.
</P>
<P>
Musavi said that regional cooperation is the ultimate way out
for the countries in the region.
</P>
<P>
He also expressed the belief that Pakistan, Iran, Turkey and
Central Asia is a visible globe for furthering regional
cooperation. 
